Kataklysm - Of Ghosts And Gods (Deluxe) [Metal] (2015) (mp3)

ataklysm is a Canadian death metal band. They call their musical style "northern hyperblast" after an advertisement in M.E.A.T. magazine describing another band, Fear Factory, as "hyperblast". The term refers to the extremely fast blast beats that former Kataklysm's drummer, Max Duhamel, fuses into the music.
